{"tid":812003,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"勸各位巴打，千祈唔好揀成日睇韓劇既女仔😪😢","createTime":"2018-09-09T09:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T10:35:57.000Z","uid":197813,"like":29,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"17ecaeaa476c304bea0a0d885b9f0c62765a17e8","tid":812003,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:56:33.000Z","msg":"各位巴打，如果你條女成日睇韓劇表示左咩？ 表示你好快會俾人飛<br />\n<br />\n點解？以前既韓劇既愛情片好撚浪漫，條女會問你點解唔會好撚似個男主角咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁算，依樣野起碼我做到，身為一個有心思既巴打既我&hellip;會做到小驚喜製造浪漫氣氛出黎，雖然唔會有電視劇咁有煙花&hellip;有閃燈&hellip;有雪落，但都可以哄到你女朋友開心。<br />\n<br />\n只從我條女開始睇完套繼承者們就開始痴線，今次就會問你點解人地咁靚仔又有錢，我心諗，屌你老母點解依家既韓劇男主角個個設定都係有錢&hellip;有背景&hellip;有家底&hellip;又要生到咁靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nOk無問題錢依家野可以慢慢搵俾條女，就算搵唔到成億都搵到幾百萬掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有樓有車都勉強可以做到，樣子你都可以解釋韓國出名整容 <br />\n<br />\n屌！跟住佢又睇完套乜鳩來自猩猩的你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依套劇真係害撚死人 <br />\n主角靚仔有錢不在話，今次仲要有超能力，無錯，個主角係外星人&hellip;仲要有超能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次條女問你點解唔似男主角咁 ？？屌！港女係咪睇撚到傻撚左？ 浪漫我可以製造，錢我可以搵，樣我可以整 ，屌你，超能力我邊撚到整到俾你睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以提醒各位巴打見到你條女睇韓劇要小心 <br />\n佢會好快飛左你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf868fb092bb4073343d19364492192b7172f1b","tid":812003,"uid":178853,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:58:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0d3c8ce4aed945948ffac61b21aae895c464186","tid":812003,"uid":197813,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6cf868fb092bb4073343d19364492192b7172f1b","tid":812003,"uid":178853,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:58:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:59:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49040266ec4a81839d060e28123ed31414ab2acc","tid":812003,"uid":127292,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T10:00:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5971018d52cd47b103c5b885cf65613c88d401ad","tid":812003,"uid":199633,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T10:01:37.000Z","msg":"睇得都係無腦港女日日FF自己有條仔靚仔又有錢有家底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n編劇戇鳩<br />\n睇果個仲戇鳩<br />\n呢啲女要唔要都罷啦"},{"pid":"4ebb047b5afb3f56c6838960f8c48243ac111501","tid":812003,"uid":89608,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T10:05:22.000Z","msg":"樓主咁辛苦作個故仔出黎踩低下港女, 等班仇女既連登仔又有機會發洩,<br />\n真係叻仔"},{"pid":"8ef1fb98fdd42255d2e650ca9763d5d17c0fc1c9","tid":812003,"uid":64155,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5971018d52cd47b103c5b885cf65613c88d401ad","tid":812003,"uid":199633,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T10:01:37.000Z","msg":"睇得都係無腦港女日日FF自己有條仔靚仔又有錢有家底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n編劇戇鳩<br />\n睇果個仲戇鳩<br />\n呢啲女要唔要都罷啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T10:06:00.000Z","msg":"啱<br />\n啲臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <i